column2: Original ICQ Data with Reasons Points were Removed
This is a dataset of comet C/1995 O1 (Hale Bopp) visual magnitudes that was compiled from 17 observers submissions to the International Comet Quarterly
column3: appended with a list detailing why data were removed from the final datasets. Please see supplementary document for definitions of each column in ICQs data format.
